        "type": "stat_block",
        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "Typically created by wizards who are hobbyists or professional architects, an *architect's pattern book* allows the caster to customize certain spells that create magical structures or domiciles, adding recreational areas such as an indoor bathhouse, gaming room, swimming pool, or similar luxury.",
