                    "action_type": {
                        "type": "stat_block_section",
                        "subtype": "action_type",
                        "name": "Free Action"
                    },
                    "frequency": "once per week",
                    "effect": "If your next action is to cast a  *cozy cabin* ,  *planar palace* , or  *resplendent mansion* spell, you add a room to the structure that is up to 10 feet per side per rank of the spell. This room is outfitted with all the accoutrements for a particular type of recreation, determined by you when you cast the spell. Any character who spends at least 1 hour using this recreational facility and then sleeps a full 8 hours inside the location created by the spell is exceptionally well-rested. They regain double the amount of Hit Points they would normally receive for an 8-hour rest, and when they make the next day\u2019s preparations, they gain a +1 circumstance bonus to Athletics checks and Will saves for the next 12 hours.",
